text: Greg McLay (born 7 May 1969) is an Australian cricketer. He played six first- class matches for New South Wales in 1990/91. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Wagga Wagga
